theorem image.lift_fac (F' : MonoFactorisation f) : «expr ≫ » (image.lift F') F'.m = image.ι f :=
  by
  ext x
  change («expr ≫ » F'.e F'.m) _ = _
  rw [F'.fac, (classical.indefinite_description _ x.2).2]
  rfl
#align image.lift_fac image.lift_fac

  by
  ext
  rfl
